{"subject":"IRS","year":2015,"question":"The Hadith \"The best of people are those who are most beneficial to people\" is from:","options":[\"Sahih al-Bukhari\",\"Sahih Muslim\",\"Sunan al-Tirmidhi\",\"Sunan Abu Dawud\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"It is recorded by al-Tirmidhi and others."},
{"subject":"IRS","year":2016,"question":"The Hadith \"A true believer does not taunt, curse, or use obscene language\" is from:","options":[\"Sahih al-Bukhari\",\"Sahih Muslim\",\"Sunan al-Tirmidhi\",\"Sunan Ibn Majah\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"It is found in Sahih al-Bukhari."},
