{"subject":"IRS","year":2020,"question":"The Hadith \"The best of people are the most beneficial to people\" is a:","options":[\"Prophetic maxim\",\"Quranic verse\",\"Fiqh ruling\",\"Moral philosophy\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"It is a Prophetic saying."},
{"subject":"IRS","year":2021,"question":"The Hadith \"A person is not a believer who eats his fill while his neighbour is hungry\" is from:","options":[\"Sahih al-Bukhari\",\"Sahih Muslim\",\"Sunan al-Tirmidhi\",\"Sunan Ibn Majah\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"It is in Sahih al-Bukhari."},
