{"subject":"IRS","year":2023,"question":"The Hadith \"Religion is sincerity (nasihah)\" was said in response to a question about:","options":[\"The meaning of religion\",\"The nature of faith\",\"The Day of Judgment\",\"The law\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The companion asked about the essence of religion."},
