{"subject":"IRS","year":2025,"question":"The Hadith \"The first to be judged on the Day of Resurrection is the martyr\" warns against:","options":[\"Showing off and seeking fame in deeds\",\"Fearing death\",\"Loving the world\",\"Disobeying parents\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The hadith warns that martyrs who fought for fame will be punished."},
